sentence: what is the longest river in the state with the highest point ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the longest river in the state with the highest point ?
sql: select river.river_name from river , highlow where river.traverse = highlow.state_name and highlow.highest_elevation = ( select max ( highlow.highest_elevation ) from highlow ) order by river.length desc limit 1 ;
